(1692, 'elementor_remote_info_feed_data', 'a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:48:\"How To Embed Video In WordPress (YouTube + More)\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:117:\"Learn about all the ways with which you can embed video in WordPress, including videos for private membership sites. \";s:7:\"created\";i:1598963402;s:5:\"badge\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:121:\"https://elementor.com/blog/embed-video-wordpress/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}i:1;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:70:\"Elementor Team Writes: How To Create a Complete Web Design Style Guide\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:290:\"When designing a website, it’s critical that everyone uses the same visual language in order to achieve a consistent and cohesive end result. This is where the Style Guide comes into play. In this article, our Product Designer discusses why and how you should create your own style guide.\";s:7:\"created\";i:1598957678;s:5:\"badge\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:122:\"https://elementor.com/blog/web-design-style-guide/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}i:2;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:34:\"Complete Guide to WordPress Themes\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:233:\"If you\'re using WordPress, you need to understand the concept of WordPress themes. Themes are an essential part of your website and you won\'t be able to get the most from WordPress if you don\'t know what themes are and how they work.\";s:7:\"created\";i:1598529207;s:5:\"badge\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:116:\"https://elementor.com/blog/wordpress-themes/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}i:3;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:67:\"Is WordPress Hard to Use? Sometimes, But It\'s Worth It (Here\'s Why)\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:267:\"Along with the challenges of working with WordPress, there are many benefits that make it the leading platform for web creators. In this post, we discuss both sides and share some strategies that will help you make it easier to create awesome websites with WordPress.\";s:7:\"created\";i:1597914309;s:5:\"badge\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:124:\"https://elementor.com/blog/is-wordpress-hard-to-use/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}i:4;a:5:{s:5:\"title\";s:60:\"Monthly Template Kits #40: The Flooring Website Template Kit\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:223:\"This month’s template kit is for flooring companies looking to build a sophisticated, attractive website, which can also be used by other business-types, such as spa websites, medical clinics, law offices, and many more. \";s:7:\"created\";i:1597824062;s:5:\"badge\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:129:\"https://elementor.com/blog/flooring-website-template-kit/?utm_source=wp-overview-widget&utm_medium=wp-dash&utm_campaign=news-feed\";}}', 'no'),
